{"parse":{"title":"Hands up punishment","pageid":41920178,"revid":843749639,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-move\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Wikibooks-logo.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wikibooks logo\"><img alt=\"Wikibooks logo\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikibooks-logo.svg/48px-Wikibooks-logo.svg.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikibooks-logo.svg/72px-Wikibooks-logo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikibooks-logo.svg/96px-Wikibooks-logo.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"300\" data-file-height=\"300\" /></a></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\">This article <b>has now been successfully <a href=\"https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/WB:IMPORT\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"b:WB:IMPORT\">imported</a> to <a href=\"/wiki/Wikibooks\" title=\"Wikibooks\">Wikibooks</a> under the name <a href=\"https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Transwiki:Hands_up_punishment\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"b:Transwiki:Hands up punishment\">Hands up punishment</a>.</b><span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> If this page can be <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:EDIT\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wikipedia:EDIT\">rewritten</a> into an encyclopedic article, please do so and remove this message and/or add a link to the Wikibook using &#123;&#123;<a href=\"/wiki/Template:Wikibooks\" title=\"Template:Wikibooks\">wikibooks</a>&#125;&#125;.</span></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-globalize\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><img alt=\"Globe icon.\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Ambox_globe_content.svg/48px-Ambox_globe_content.svg.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Ambox_globe_content.svg/73px-Ambox_globe_content.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Ambox_globe_content.svg/97px-Ambox_globe_content.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"350\" data-file-height=\"290\" /></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\">The examples and perspective in this article <b>deal primarily with the Indian subcontinent and do not represent a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Countering_systemic_bias\" title=\"Wikipedia:WikiProject Countering systemic bias\">worldwide view</a> of the subject</b>.<span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> You may <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Hands_up_punishment&amp;action=edit\">improve this article</a>, discuss the issue on the <a href=\"/wiki/Talk:Hands_up_punishment\" title=\"Talk:Hands up punishment\">talk page</a>, or <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Article_wizard\" title=\"Wikipedia:Article wizard\">create a new article</a>, as appropriate.</span>  <small><i>(June 2017)</i></small><small class=\"hide-when-compact\"><i> (<a href=\"/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal\" title=\"Help:Maintenance template removal\">Learn how and when to remove this template message</a>)</i></small></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Schoolboy gets punished.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/44/Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg/220px-Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"301\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/44/Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg/330px-Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/44/Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"439\" data-file-height=\"601\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Schoolboy_gets_punished.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>hands up punishment</b> is a form of punishment given in schools of the <a href=\"/wiki/Indian_subcontinent\" title=\"Indian subcontinent\">Indian subcontinent</a>, especially in <a href=\"/wiki/India\" title=\"India\">India</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Bangladesh\" title=\"Bangladesh\">Bangladesh</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Sri_Lanka\" title=\"Sri Lanka\">Sri Lanka</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Pakistan\" title=\"Pakistan\">Pakistan</a>. In this punishment, one is made to raise his or her hands above their head\u2014a <a href=\"/wiki/Stress_position\" title=\"Stress position\">stress position</a>\u2014and remain in this state for a period of time.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Identifying_reliable_sources\" title=\"Wikipedia:Identifying reliable sources\"><span title=\"The material near this tag relies on an unreliable source. self-published source: personal blog (June 2015)\">unreliable source</span></a></i>&#93;</sup> The recipient of the punishment is not permitted to join their hands above their head. The hands up position becomes painful within ten or fifteen minutes. This is generally done to correct mischievous students in schools.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Hands_up_punishment&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Psychological_torture\" title=\"Psychological torture\">Psychological torture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Urdhva_Vrikshasana\" title=\"Urdhva Vrikshasana\">Urdhva Vrikshasana</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Murga_punishment\" title=\"Murga punishment\">Murga punishment</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Hands_up_punishment&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.eslchronicle.com/12-punishment-ideas-for-teachers/\">\"12 punishment ideas for Teachers\"</a>. <i>eslchronicle.com</i>. January 11, 2012<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">February 28,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=eslchronicle.com&amp;rft.atitle=12+punishment+ideas+for+Teachers&amp;rft.date=2012-01-11&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eslchronicle.com%2F12-punishment-ideas-for-teachers%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHands+up+punishment\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1283\nCached time: 20180908095839\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.120 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.165 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 376/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 10791/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 792/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 11/40\nExpensive parser function count: 3/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 1034/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.054/10.000